* If you want to propose merging a {{strong|category}}, you must do so at [[Wikipedia:Categories for discussion]], using the specific templates available there.
* If you want to propose merging a {{strong|template}}, you must do so at [[Wikipedia:Templates for discussion]], using the specific templates available there.

